OL,3,CMan whose brother died of MND
OL,4,C'emotional' as major landmark lit up
OL,5,Cin his memory
OL,7,FThe bridge will once again be lit up
OL,8,Fblue and orange on Saturday night in
OL,9,Fmemory of Rob.
OL,11,F"When I saw it last year, I cried."
OL,12,Fsaid Tom.
OL,14,F"It was strange to know I had somehow
OL,15,Fmanaged to achieve that and it felt
OL,16,Flike I had done some good.
OL,18,F"I hope to get it lit up every year.
OL,19,FNot just for Robbie but for everyone
OL,20,Fwho is living with or affected somehow
OL,21,Fby MND."
