OL,3,CMan whose brother died of MND
OL,4,C'emotional' as major landmark lit up
OL,5,Cin his memory
OL,7,FRob, who dreamt of becoming a computer
OL,8,Fgames designer, was diagnosed when he
OL,9,Fwas only 24-years-old and given 2
OL,10,Fyears to live.
OL,12,FHe had initially started having issues
OL,13,Fwith the movement in his right hand
OL,14,Fwhen he couldn't move his thumb and
OL,15,Fthis is what started the long journey
OL,16,Fto diagnosis.
OL,18,FHe went on to become an active
OL,19,Fcampaigner trying to raise awareness
OL,20,Fthrough challenges.
