OL,4,C'emotional' as major landmark lit up
OL,5,Cin his memory
OL,7,FThe disease quickly stripped him of
OL,8,Fhis ability to move, and he used an
OL,9,Feye gaze device to communicate.
OL,11,FHe received a video message from Kevin
OL,12,FSinfield whilst in hospital with Rob
OL,13,FBurrow thanking him for his work
OL,14,Fraising awareness.
OL,16,FWhat is Motor Neurone Disease (MND)?
OL,18,FMND is a fatal, rapidly progressing
OL,19,Fdisease that affects the brain and
OL,20,Fspinal cord.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
