OL,4,C'emotional' as major landmark lit up
OL,5,Cin his memory
OL,7,FIt attacks the nerves that control
OL,8,Fmovement so muscles no longer work.
OL,10,FSix people are diagnosed every day
OL,11,Fwith MND in the UK. It affects more
OL,12,Fthan 5,000 adults in the UK at any one
OL,13,Ftime.
OL,15,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,16,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,17,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,18,Four region.
